snippet.title: 22 Racing Series - Steam Launch Date Announcement
snippet.description:
The world's first and fastest Future Physics Racer (FPR) and Real-Time Strategy Racer (RTS-Racing) is coming to Steam in Early Access on the 22nd November, 2022.

Hone your skills in time trials, race online in team challenge events, or join in on mass royale racing elimination and streaker modes.

Built for racers and built for modders. 22RS allows you to build your own vehicles and tracks, modify race rules and build your own tournaments so that you can race your way.

Releasing in Early Access, features will be released and expanded along with community feedback.

Join us in the racing of the future - 22 Racing Series!
